				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Grettings my fellow Rangers.
<br />
I have just successfully obtained the Coldain Hero's Insignia Ring. My guild mates are already asking if I plan on trying for the Ring of Dain Frostreaver, aka 10th Coldain Ring. I have decided that I will so I am looking for all the information that I can find on how to accomplish this daunting task. If any of you fine players have any info on successes or failures, I would be grateful if you would please share it with me. I am looking for a sound plan of battle and any tips on how to command an army of people to victory. Also do you lose the 9th ring or the Dirk of the Dain if you fail. So many questions I have. 
<br />
Safe Journeys<br />_________________<br />He's one of them Rangers, dangerous folk they are wandering the wilds....
